node.detail_zh: 患者過往健康良好，2 月 5 日至 6 月 27 曾到印度，6 月 27 日開始頭痛，返港後由檢疫中心送院，與第 #1199 宗個案患者有關連。
node.detail_en: The patient has good past health and was in India between Feb 5 12 and June 27. On June 27, he started having headaches. He was transferred to hospital from the quarantine centre after returning to Hong Kong. His case is epidemiologically linked to the case of patient #1199.
